Supporting Members
The Linux Foundation itself benefits from the support of a global membership of over 1,000 members.
The Linux Foundation community of projects remains financially strong thanks to the support of nearly
2,000 global member organizations across all our project communities and entities. The diversity of our
membership community means no single member accounts for more than 2% of the financial support
received this year.
The Linux Foundation has made many investments to spread the benefits of open source throughout the
world, and that has yielded strong support from countries including China, Japan, Germany, the UK, India,
Canada, France, and Switzerland.
